description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene (Bacillus a; Bacillus casei a; Bacterium casei a; Caseobacterium vulgare; Lactobacillus casei; Lactobacillus casei subsp. casei; Lactobacterium casei; Streptobacterium casei.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
